          .buy__main__buyinfo__content__card__upper
            .buy__main__buyinfo__content__card__upper__detail
              支払い方法
            .buy__main__buyinfo__content__card__upper__change
              =link_to "#" do
                .buy__main__buyinfo__content__card__upper__change__text
